s of Main TV & Child TV and respective end date of plans will continue to remain same.\n                                    \n                                    C. You can do SWAP STB in case both the plans of both STBs are inactive.\n                                    \n                                    D. However, SWAP will fail in case the plans of Parent and Child TV are different (eg if one is Royal & other is Prime).\n                                    \n                                    E. In case any of the STB or both STBs are in suspended status, SWAP will fail.', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'Do You Want To Continue ?', '', 'Message', '', '', '', 'Swap', '', 'STB ID :', '', 'New STB ID :', '', '', '', 'Reason :', 'Select Reason\n\t\tSD to HD Upgrade\n\t\tFaulty STB Replace\n\t\tUpgrade to PVR\n\t\tCustomer Request for New STB\n\t\tOthers', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', '', '', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'STB ID', ':', '', 'New STB ID', ':', '', 'Reason', ':', '', '', '', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'Do You Want To Continue ?', '', 'TERMINATE', '', 'STB/MAC ID :', '', 'VC/MAC ID :', '', 'Reason :', 'Select Reason\n\t\tCustomer Shifted to Different Location\n\t\tCustomers Request - Shifted to DTH\n\t\tCustomers Request - Service Issue\n\t\tCustomers Request - Price Issue\n\t\tOthers', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'STB/MAC ID', ':', '', 'VC/MAC ID', ':', '', 'Reason', ':', '', '', '', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'Are You Sure?\n                                    \n                                    You Want To Terminate', '', '', '', '', 'Confirmation', '', 'Are You Sure?\n                                    \n                                    Do you want to align the expiry date with your Basic Plan ?', '', '', '', '', '*taxes extra', 'OTP', '', 'Please Enter OTP', '', '', 'Customer Record', '', '', '', '', '', 'Transaction Status', '', '', '', '', 'Transaction History', '', '', '', '', 'Add Plan Pack Status', '', '', '', '', 'Add Plan Cart', '', '', 'D