                                                                 *', '', '', '', 'Data Prevention Act Popup', '', '1', 'I, the undersigned, agree that I have been sufficiently informed in advance by the Company about submitting the Personal Data (as defined in the Act) in physical or digital form (“Personal Data”) for establishing proof of identification and address and use my photo and other demographic details (name, gender, date of birth, address etc.) for the purposes of entering into Agreements/provision of services and payments if required. (“Purpose).', '2', 'I understand and consent that, my Personal Data that will be sought and provided to the Company may be used in relation to provision of its services and other legal requirements in the manner as the Company may deem fit and proper.', '3', 'I, hereby declare that all the information have been voluntarily furnished by me and is true, correct, and complete. I will not hold the Company or any of its officials responsible in case of any incorrect information provided by me.', '4', 'I, further confirm that the purpose of collecting my Personal Data has been duly explained to me in my local language and wherein I have also been duly described about the provision of withdrawal of consent and process for redressal of grievances if any pertaining to use of my personal data.  The Company has informed that my personal data any other information submitted to the Company herewith shall not be used/stored/shared for any purpose other than for the purpose explained to me/verification, or as per requirements of law.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'OTP', '', '', '', 'Resend OTP', '', '', 'OTP', '', '', '', 'Resend OTP', '', 'Message', '', 'Are you sure you want to clear?', '', 'RMN validation of this Network is pending', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Session Expiring!', '', 'Your Portal Session is going to Expire in\xa052\xa0seconds.\n                                                                        Please click on YES if you wish to continue.', '']
